author: Jessica
title: Urban Decay Brow Box Only $9 Shipped (Regularly $30)
text:
Hurry on over to UrbanDecay.com where they have their Brow Box on sale for just $9 (regularly $30) – choose from Brown Sugar or Honey Pot! This highly-rated Brow Box comes with two shades of brow color, wax, tweezers and two brushes.
This is a great deal at under $10 seeing as how Sephora currently has this box priced at $30.
Even sweeter, ALL UD Beauty Junkies members get FREE shipping with every order – no minimum; otherwise, shipping is free on $50. Or, you may be able to score free 2-day shipping with ShopRunner with a $25+ order.
(Thanks, Dana!)
